data.text:
Careers

The CPRA team is comprised of hard-working and dedicated individuals from many disciplines — scientists, project managers, engineers, attorneys, accountants and other administrative professionals. From time to time, we may need to add to our team or fill a vacancy. When that happens, the job listing will be posted below. For more information, visit the Louisiana State Civil Service website.
